article.headline: Leach scores 21, Fairfield takes down Siena 88-64
article.description: — Jalen Leach scored 21 points as Fairfield beat Siena 88-64 on Sunday.
article.linkText: Leach scores 21, Fairfield takes down Siena 88-64
article.story: FAIRFIELD, Conn. -- — Jalen Leach scored 21 points as Fairfield beat Siena 88-64 on Sunday. Leach added nine rebounds for the Stags (18-10, 12-5 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Brycen Goodine was 4 of 6 shooting, including 3 for 5 from 3-point range, and went 4 for 5 from the line to add 15 points. Caleb Fields had 14 points and was 5 of 11 shooting (4 for 8 from 3-point range). Mason Courtney led the way for the Saints (4-23, 3-13) with 13 points and seven rebounds. Brendan Coyle added 13 points for Siena. Giovanni Emejuru also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
